      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in showroom-perfect condition, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of its class. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, reflects a history of uncompromising care and meticulous maintenance. This is an investment-grade example that delivers a factory-fresh experience. We invite you to experience this level of quality firsthand.",
