      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a dream sculpted from steel and chrome. This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a portal to an era of effortless sophistication. Every curve tells a story of midnight drives along the coast, and every stitch in the supple leather whispers of artisan craftsmanship. To drive this masterpiece is to command the very essence of the open road, feeling the pulse of a machine that refuses to age. It sits before you as a shimmering time capsule, a rare jewel that has been preserved with the utmost reverence. This is more than a purchase\u2014it is an inheritance of legacy, style, and soul.",
